title: Faroe Agreement
author: LLE2
pages:
#- In exchange for Protectorate Status The Islands of Faroe agree to provide the Nation of Chanada Resources:§0
§0
§0Titanium§0
§0Steel§0
§0Mercury§0
§0Platinum§0
§0
§0------->
#- Chanada will provide military protection for the Island of Faroe. Chanada will supply Faroe with Iron Reinforced Obsidian to further protect the citizens of Faroe.§0
§0Citizens of Faroe are free to enter Chanada land claims and make use of farm lands and
#- city markets. Citizens of Faroe will be permitted work visas and be able to work on Chanadian projects for payment.§0
§0
§0Faroe enemies are considered Chanada's enemies and will be vaulted for cries commited against Faroe.
#- Agreement is sealed apon signing this autism document.§0
§0
